# AI Agent Global Rules

# 1. ALWAYS READ agents.md FIRST
# The root `agents.md` file contains the definitive project configuration, architecture,
# and instructions on how to use AI skills in this repository.
# Do not start generating code or planning without first checking `agents.md`.

# 2. Use the Skills System
# Read the relevant skill files from `.agents/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md`
# based on the technologies requested in the prompt.
